data.description: 🏡 ‼️ ALL OFFERS DUE TODAY NLT 6pm 2/25/2024 ‼️ 🏡  From the moment you arrive, you'll be excited by the inviting ambiance of this remarkable residence. With its airy, open floor plan and abundant natural light, this home welcomes you with open arms. The modern kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting gleaming granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and double ovens for effortless entertaining. The seamless flow between the kitchen and great room creates a space that's perfect for gathering with loved ones. Outside, the beautiful deck is ready for some summertime fun and relaxation. The master bedroom provides a cozy sanctuary, complete with two spacious walk-in closets and a stylish master bathroom including a soaking tub. Downstairs, the oversized recreation room offers endless possibilities, whether you're seeking a quiet escape or a place to host game nights with friends. Rest easy with an attached garage to protect your vehicle from the outside elements. The resident community amenities include a pool and clubhouse for all ages. This home and location truly has it all.   Located just minutes from Andrews Joint Base and Interstate 495, with easy access to D.C., this could be the perfect place to call home. Don't miss your chance – schedule a showing today and make this exquisite home yours!!
